gate: OPEN
task: S74-TD4
title: Remove Outline from Map Direction Arrows
description: |
  Remove the outline/stroke from direction arrows on maps:
  - Locate the arrow components used for vehicle/track direction
  - Remove or set stroke/outline to transparent
  - Ensure arrows use only the track color fill
  - Test on all map instances (object screen, tracking, history)
  - Verify arrows remain visible and clear without outline

acceptance:
  - Direction arrows have no outline or stroke
  - Arrows use solid fill with track color only
  - Arrows remain clearly visible on all map backgrounds
  - Consistent appearance across all map screens

requires: []
estimated: 1 hour
